====主要参数====
*'''editpage''' – 默认情况下，“编辑”链接将应用于名为[[/]]的页面。使用此参数可以指定编辑的其他页面。This will normally be the page where the {{tlx|Box-header}} is used.
*'''noedit''' – 默认情况下，“编辑”链接显示在右侧。设定{{para|noedit|yes}}（或任何不为空的值）以隐藏链接。如果{{para|EDITLINK}}非空值，则“编辑”链接也将被隐藏。
*'''section''' – 默认情况下，“编辑”链接将应用于整个页面。使用此参数可以指定特定段落的编号，例如{{para|section|2}}。
*'''title''' – 框的标题，例如{{para|title|Portals}}
*'''top''' – extra text to display after the "edit" and "view" links. Hidden if {{para|EDITLINK}} is non-blank.
*'''viewpage''' – if non-blank, this should be a valid Wikipedia page name, it creates a "view" link after the "edit" link. Hidden if {{para|EDITLINK}} is non-blank.

====Behaviour options====
*'''EDIT''' – by default, all section edit links are suppressed. Set {{para|EDIT|yes}} (or any non-blank value) to override this.
*'''EDITLINK''' – set {{para|EDITLINK|no}} (or any non-blank value) to hide the "edit" and "view" links, and the text after those
*'''SPAN''' – by default, the box title is enclosed in {{tag|h2}} tags. Set {{para|SPAN|yes}} (or any non-blank value) to use {{tag|span}} tags instead.
*'''TOC''' – by default, the table of contents is suppressed. Set {{para|TOC|yes}} (or any non-blank value) to override this.

